<sect1 id="group__io__module_1io_overview_mod">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The IO module provides functionality for reading and writing data files, including ROOT files and HDF5 storage.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__io__module_1io_formats_mod">
<title>Supported Formats</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>ROOT files</bold>: Reading physics data from ROOT TTrees</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>HDF5 files</bold>: Storing processed graphs and tensors</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classio" kindref="compound">io</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
</sect1>
